<P>
Alan B. Lefkof, senior vice president-finance and corporate development at Grid 
Systems Corp., has been named president of Grid, a computer manufacturer based 
in Fremont, Calif. Lefkof, 36, succeeds Samuel J. Wiegand, 60, who announced 
recently that he will retire at the year's end. 
