<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORE MEDFLY SPRAYING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
This continuous spraying of our population with poisonous substances is like 
killing the chickens in order to keep the coop clean! 
</P>
<P>
Granted, the Medfly infestation is a serious problem. But if we possess the 
technology to land men on the moon, surely we can devise a less-hazardous 
method of eradication. Any politician supporting aerial spraying of malathion 
will certainly not get my vote. 
</P>
<P>
VIVO BENNETT 
</P>
<P>
Los Angeles 
