ROMANIA; MASSACRES -- ROMANIA; ROMANIA -- GOVERNMENT; ROMANIA -- FOREIGN 
RELATIONS -- USSR; SHEVARDNADZE, EDUARD A; CEAUSESCU, NICOLAE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
