FAILURES: Lincoln Savings &amp; Loan of Irvine (A3, D5), now target of a state 
criminal investigation, has hardly been the only Orange County thrift to go 
under. . . . In the last four years, 13 other S&amp;Ls based here have failed 
-- more than in any other California county. Ten county banks failed this 
decade, also a high in the state. Dana Parsons and Mark I. Pinsky 
