<TEXT>
<P>
Outfielder John Kruk has signed a 1990 contract for $615,000 plus bonuses with 
the Philadelphia Phillies, General Manager Lee Thomas announced today. 
</P>
<P>
The Phillies also announced that pitcher Marvin Freeman and outfielder Ron 
Jones have been assigned to the Scranton-Wilkes-Barre Red Barons of the 
